        "text": "A minimalist, heavy solid black icon of a singular amuse-bouche nested within the curve of an elegant tasting spoon. Side profile. Highly simplified linocut print aesthetic with a heavy visual weight. Most of the spoon handle and the amuse form a single, substantial black mass. Thick, bold white negative space is used only to define the rim of the spoon's bowl and a single, simple arc and three small white specks to define the texture and structure of the delicate amuse. High-contrast, no fine lines, heavy visual weight. Solid stencil isolated on white. Optimized for a clean, single-boolean SVG shape.",
